{"id": "ChIJO53j58ikwoARyIQAbNStag4", "rating": 4.6, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 1756, "displayName": {"text": "Sidecar Doughnuts & Coffee", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Sleek sweet shop for creative donuts, from sweet flavors to savory breakfast versions, plus coffee.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJO53j58ikwoARyIQAbNStag4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25saVZWVlBXVmh2VWpOc1JrVmtURVpNTVdsME0wRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Best donuts on planet earth. My god are they expensive but they are worth it. I've been eating them for almost ten years and when they have it, the salted malted chocolate chip cookie dough donut is peak. I love this place and it's always worth your time. Coffee is fine, the workers are wonderful, and the dough is the best. Oh and the eggs bene donut?? DIVINE", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Best donuts on planet earth. My god are they expensive but they are worth it. I've been eating them for almost ten years and when they have it, the salted malted chocolate chip cookie dough donut is peak. I love this place and it's always worth your time. Coffee is fine, the workers are wonderful, and the dough is the best. Oh and the eggs bene donut?? DIVINE", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "The Breakfast King", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116328908550327319783/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxvMXTnC7aJnIUyc1-tEfWmpb-MhLx_GGy387SKkM6E0EJehI=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-05T20:06:30.998202071Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25saVZWVlBXVmh2VWpOc1JrVmtURVpNTVdsME0wRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25saVZWVlBXVmh2VWpOc1JrVmtURVpNTVdsME0wRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2a4c8e7e39d3b:0xe6aadd46c0084c8"}, {"name": "places/ChIJO53j58ikwoARyIQAbNStag4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSUGMwZEZRVXQyUzBSMldtMVBWR0ZEWlRsWk5sRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "For the love of doughnuts!!! 😊 Stopped by for brunch and was immediately overwhelmed in the best way possible by the huge selection of doughnuts. Finally decided on the rotating ring doughnut paired with a vanilla latte, and it did not disappoint! Fresh, flavorful, and the perfect sweet treat. Definitely a spot worth coming back to", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "For the love of doughnuts!!! 😊 Stopped by for brunch and was immediately overwhelmed in the best way possible by the huge selection of doughnuts. Finally decided on the rotating ring doughnut paired with a vanilla latte, and it did not disappoint! Fresh, flavorful, and the perfect sweet treat. Definitely a spot worth coming back to", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Tokunbo P", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111662365162458877153/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDOFGJwwsxBu5dN81FttIVRlozpDLAa_lU9WidiiQbzaL0RYac=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-08T20:11:12.717973096Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSUGMwZEZRVXQyUzBSMldtMVBWR0ZEWlRsWk5sRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSUGMwZEZRVXQyUzBSMldtMVBWR0ZEWlRsWk5sRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2a4c8e7e39d3b:0xe6aadd46c0084c8"}, {"name": "places/ChIJO53j58ikwoARyIQAbNStag4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGalpXbHlhelEzZVZwaWVIUm9UVTk2U0RWWWEwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This spot is an absolute vibe! 🔥 If you’re looking for basic donuts, this ain't it. Sidecar's flavors are insanely creative and straight up bussin'. Every single bite totally slaps, no cap. They have everything from super sweet to savory options. I grabbed a few to share with my friends, paired them with their iced coffee, and the combo was legit fire.\n\nThe shop itself has a super sleek, modern aesthetic, making it a dope place to hang out or snap some aesthetic pics for the gram. For the $10 - $20 price range, you are getting premium, top tier quality that is 100% worth the cash.\n\nThe crew behind the counter was super chill and the service was fast, even when busy. Plus, it's super convenient since they offer dine in, takeout, and even no contact delivery if you're just wanting to rot in bed.\n\nIf you haven't checked this place out yet, you're seriously sleeping on the best donuts in town. 10/10 would recommend! 🍩✨", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This spot is an absolute vibe! 🔥 If you’re looking for basic donuts, this ain't it. Sidecar's flavors are insanely creative and straight up bussin'. Every single bite totally slaps, no cap. They have everything from super sweet to savory options. I grabbed a few to share with my friends, paired them with their iced coffee, and the combo was legit fire.\n\nThe shop itself has a super sleek, modern aesthetic, making it a dope place to hang out or snap some aesthetic pics for the gram. For the $10 - $20 price range, you are getting premium, top tier quality that is 100% worth the cash.\n\nThe crew behind the counter was super chill and the service was fast, even when busy. Plus, it's super convenient since they offer dine in, takeout, and even no contact delivery if you're just wanting to rot in bed.\n\nIf you haven't checked this place out yet, you're seriously sleeping on the best donuts in town. 10/10 would recommend! 🍩✨", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ophelia Guzman", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114943927690334193227/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJb4J2vEvk6MXikmjeEVsUVc2XI1eAaaOCRPdJZxKRGcjgyiw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-20T11:49:08.133340630Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGalpXbHlhelEzZVZwaWVIUm9UVTk2U0RWWWEwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGalpXbHlhelEzZVZwaWVIUm9UVTk2U0RWWWEwRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2a4c8e7e39d3b:0xe6aadd46c0084c8"}, {"name": "places/ChIJO53j58ikwoARyIQAbNStag4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT205RlVXbEdiRjlaZEVJeWNIUmxVWEZJVjJsbFpHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Donut mind me… just eating some delicious donuts. This place is something else. We are @sidecardoughnuts in Santa Monica. We tried the following:\n\nBanana Bread Latte-\nOur Banana Bread Latte starts with our rich, smooth premium espresso, swirled with our house-made banana bread syrup, topped with your choice of milk (hot or iced) and a sprinkle of candied walnuts.\n\nBasil Eggs Benedict-\nOur Malasada-style doughnut filled with poached egg, Benton’s Country Ham, and a house made basil hollandaise sauce.\n\nMaple Bacon-\nRaised doughnut topped with pure Vermont Maple Syrup glaze and crispy, all-natural bacon.\n\nButter & Salt-\nVanilla bean cake doughnut with brown butter glaze and fleur de sel.\n\nThe latte taste just like banana bread!! I love it. The eggs benedict donut is so different than anything I have ever had in a very good way. It was salty, eggy, savory, and eggcelent. I have a picture of it cut in half for you to see! The bacon on the maple bacon was really good quality. It had great maple flavor as well. We got the butter and salt to get a fairly basic donut to really taste the dough itself. It is great. They were all fresh and the shop has such an intoxicating aroma.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Donut mind me… just eating some delicious donuts. This place is something else. We are @sidecardoughnuts in Santa Monica. We tried the following:\n\nBanana Bread Latte-\nOur Banana Bread Latte starts with our rich, smooth premium espresso, swirled with our house-made banana bread syrup, topped with your choice of milk (hot or iced) and a sprinkle of candied walnuts.\n\nBasil Eggs Benedict-\nOur Malasada-style doughnut filled with poached egg, Benton’s Country Ham, and a house made basil hollandaise sauce.\n\nMaple Bacon-\nRaised doughnut topped with pure Vermont Maple Syrup glaze and crispy, all-natural bacon.\n\nButter & Salt-\nVanilla bean cake doughnut with brown butter glaze and fleur de sel.\n\nThe latte taste just like banana bread!! I love it. The eggs benedict donut is so different than anything I have ever had in a very good way. It was salty, eggy, savory, and eggcelent. I have a picture of it cut in half for you to see! The bacon on the maple bacon was really good quality. It had great maple flavor as well. We got the butter and salt to get a fairly basic donut to really taste the dough itself. It is great. They were all fresh and the shop has such an intoxicating aroma.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "CheffreyApproved", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104169983426523303580/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4wtQzC6Xqyx2R9-PLdV1k0D_lnNXt97ZFdDq_6Wq1uMsrW3o=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-25T20:09:05.309464124Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT205RlVXbEdiRjlaZEVJeWNIUmxVWEZJVjJsbFpHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT205RlVXbEdiRjlaZEVJeWNIUmxVWEZJVjJsbFpHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2a4c8e7e39d3b:0xe6aadd46c0084c8"}, {"name": "places/ChIJO53j58ikwoARyIQAbNStag4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOcFlrUndWR3Q0UzBSRGVGZDRVbU5FU0U4Mk5GRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Love this place, fresh, warm doughnuts with that crisp edge and soft center, exactly what you want. Coffee was good too. Easy stop before the beach, parking can be tricky during rush hours, staff was upbeat and the shop seems clean, will happily come back", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Love this place, fresh, warm doughnuts with that crisp edge and soft center, exactly what you want. Coffee was good too. Easy stop before the beach, parking can be tricky during rush hours, staff was upbeat and the shop seems clean, will happily come back", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Lillian Delalama", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117567488799328465462/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJRlyJDeR_v8D1YOlrnHVyK7d61hEeSyPTfUuRAIJ-6AvJhqA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-24T06:15:37.773003297Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOcFlrUndWR3Q0UzBSRGVGZDRVbU5FU0U4Mk5GRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOcFlrUndWR3Q0UzBSRGVGZDRVbU5FU0U4Mk5GRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2a4c8e7e39d3b:0xe6aadd46c0084c8"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJO53j58ikwoARyIQAbNStag4/photos/AWCwydgEz8BwFp0e1XBr-KrT9msJc2PCpWs1RyqOC5deaDvpox4p7DYpoVaJ0C2A5L80v8VCtJAnGEvnLgHRCzFVcS0jbWjQ-SuA2ZkxN9Nlm2rtl3RQ9wtiSJpHHbw5QavHRFTh7NUjckKvfPzWXrJzmcyxJrnqM5Qq3IJHq3HFR43BbB7Qeov_D_lVMcEvzHkTvVyhwjwQ-x48htRvdTGmUXUKzB0SPXo3wHiptvXEmpeoJk-Fff2SOgFWBwLs9aysK10hN21rwiJ4WNhtyI-xFt_j1C2yALzP39vpOa3O_4z9Mj3rkaQKnbdGW3numdKaQayQ3hxzEr4Wv2R0eplQHjhlXhiQUMvgyoTw6L19vVerFq8SJxPJ-WkjUt5DrNVV9c75xPHvpLbkT4gzkjQ9eUmZTjMmxSC0Kbp6shGECN2XFNMW", "widthPx": 4032, "heightPx": 3024, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Thiago Oliveira", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/102674440447461131714", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleuser